        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " —",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": " incense yet in the high places — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Old corruptions are not eradicated without difficulty, especially when they have formerly had the patronage of those that were good, as the high places had of Samuel, Solomon, and some others. Indeed this error was so deeply rooted, that the best of their kings, till Hezekiah’s time, connived at it.",
